Our client, a well-established investment firm to invite high caliber candidates to join their company.

Responsibilities:

Leading Institutional Sales team for daily operations;
Maintain and build the business relationship with the above institutional accounts;
Provide research service to clients, including market updates, arrange conference call and collect client’s feedback;
Coordinate roadshow and corporate access for the above clients;
Maintain smooth operations and adhere to stringent procedures and high standard of compliance;
Review client feedback periodically and propose a continuous improvement plan to enhance client satisfaction.

Requirements:

At least 8-year institutional sales trading experience;  
Degree in Economics, Finance or Business related disciplines;
Independent, attentive to details, and highly motivated;
Customer-oriented and proactive with effective communications skills;
Good team player with excellent interpersonal skills;
Excellent command of English and Chinese, Native Mandarin is preferred;

To apply, please send your detailed resume or contact Boei Yan at 3460 2012 for a confidential discussion.
Only shortlisted candidates will be notified. 
Applicants who are not contacted within two weeks may consider their applications unsuccessful.
All data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only & will be used strictly confidential.

